jobs.description:
Responsibilities
Develop and maintain automated test scripts using Cypress and Postman;  
Perform automation, regression, and manual testing to ensure software quality; 
Execute NOC operations including monitoring and analysis using Grafana, Sumo Logic SIEM,  AWS, and Postman;  
Accepting flexible working hours, attending meetings according to US hours (in return can arrive at office late the next morning); 
Capable of leading teams and coordinating work effectively.  
Requirements
Strong verbal and written communication skills;  
Worked on a Scrum/ Agile automation team is a plus;  
Strong expertise in automation testing with Cypress and API testing with Postman;
Experience with both manual and automated testing processes;  
Familiarity with NOC operations, including Grafana dashboards, Sumo Logic for security and  event management, and AWS cloud environments;  
Ability to troubleshoot and analyze system and application performance;  

Prefer Qualifications:  

Excellent problem-solving and analytical skills;  
Strong attention to detail and organizational skills;  
Effective communication and teamwork abilities.  
Benefits
Friendly and dynamic working environment. Received additional training to improve  professional skills;  
Salary depends on ability (up to 35 million VND);  
Increase salary according to work performance;  
13th month salary bonus according to work performance;  
Full benefits in accordance with current laws (health insurance, social insurance, unemployment  insurance...);  
Health care insurance when signing official labor contracts;  
Annual physical examination;  
Annual tourism …  

Working time:  

From Monday to Friday: 9:00AM to 5:30PM;  
48 hours/week (rarely work on Saturdays, except for urgent tasks). 
